{"hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/OpenSwiftUI\/documentation\/OpenSwiftUI","doc:\/\/OpenSwiftUI\/documentation\/OpenSwiftUI\/Path"]]},"schemaVersion":{"minor":3,"patch":0,"major":0},"abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"Applies the given transaction mutation function to all animations used"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"within the view."}],"variants":[{"paths":["\/documentation\/openswiftui\/path\/transaction(_:)"],"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"swift"}]}],"identifier":{"url":"doc:\/\/OpenSwiftUI\/documentation\/OpenSwiftUI\/Path\/transaction(_:)","interfaceLanguage":"swift"},"kind":"symbol","sections":[],"primaryContentSections":[{"kind":"declarations","declarations":[{"languages":["swift"],"tokens":[{"kind":"attribute","text":"nonisolated"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"keyword","text":"func"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"transaction"},{"kind":"text","text":"("},{"kind":"externalParam","text":"_"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"internalParam","text":"transform"},{"kind":"text","text":": "},{"kind":"keyword","text":"@escaping"},{"kind":"text","text":" ("},{"kind":"keyword","text":"inout"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"typeIdentifier","identifier":"doc:\/\/OpenSwiftUI\/documentation\/OpenSwiftUI\/Transaction","text":"Transaction","preciseIdentifier":"s:15OpenSwiftUICore11TransactionV"},{"kind":"text","text":") -> "},{"kind":"typeIdentifier","text":"Void","preciseIdentifier":"s:s4Voida"},{"kind":"text","text":") -> "},{"kind":"keyword","text":"some"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"typeIdentifier","identifier":"doc:\/\/OpenSwiftUI\/documentation\/OpenSwiftUI\/View","text":"View","preciseIdentifier":"s:15OpenSwiftUICore4ViewP"},{"kind":"text","text":"\n"}],"platforms":["macOS"]}]},{"kind":"parameters","parameters":[{"name":"transform","content":[{"inlineContent":[{"text":"The transformation to apply to transactions","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"within this view.","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"}]}]},{"kind":"content","content":[{"anchor":"return-value","type":"heading","level":2,"text":"Return Value"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"A view that wraps this view and applies a transformation to","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"all transactions used within the view.","type":"text"}]}]},{"kind":"content","content":[{"type":"heading","anchor":"discussion","level":2,"text":"Discussion"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"Use this modifier to change or replace the animation used in a view.","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"Consider three identical animations controlled by a","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"button that executes all three animations simultaneously:","type":"text"}]},{"type":"unorderedList","items":[{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"The first animation rotates the “Rotation” ","type":"text"},{"isActive":true,"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/OpenSwiftUI\/documentation\/OpenSwiftUI\/Text"},{"text":" view by 360","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"degrees.","type":"text"}]}]},{"content":[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"The second uses the "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"transaction(_:)"},{"type":"text","text":" modifier to change the"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"animation by adding a delay to the start of the animation"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"by two seconds and then increases the rotational speed of the"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"“Rotation\\nModified” "},{"isActive":true,"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/OpenSwiftUI\/documentation\/OpenSwiftUI\/Text"},{"type":"text","text":" view animation by a factor of 2."}],"type":"paragraph"}]},{"content":[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"The third animation uses the "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"transaction(_:)"},{"type":"text","text":" modifier to"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"replace the rotation animation affecting the “Animation\\nReplaced”"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/OpenSwiftUI\/documentation\/OpenSwiftUI\/Text","isActive":true},{"type":"text","text":" view with a spring animation."}],"type":"paragraph"}]}]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"The following code implements these animations:"}]},{"type":"codeListing","syntax":"swift","code":["struct TransactionExample: View {","    @State private var flag = false","","    var body: some View {","        VStack(spacing: 50) {","            HStack(spacing: 30) {","                Text(\"Rotation\")","                    .rotationEffect(Angle(degrees:","                                            self.flag ? 360 : 0))","","                Text(\"Rotation\\nModified\")","                    .rotationEffect(Angle(degrees:","                                            self.flag ? 360 : 0))","                    .transaction { view in","                        view.animation =","                            view.animation?.delay(2.0).speed(2)","                    }","","                Text(\"Animation\\nReplaced\")","                    .rotationEffect(Angle(degrees:","                                            self.flag ? 360 : 0))","                    .transaction { view in","                        view.animation = .interactiveSpring(","                            response: 0.60,","                            dampingFraction: 0.20,","                            blendDuration: 0.25)","                    }","            }","","            Button(\"Animate\") {","                withAnimation(.easeIn(duration: 2.0)) {","                    self.flag.toggle()","                }","            }","        }","    }","}"]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Use this modifier on leaf views such as "},{"identifier":"doc:\/\/OpenSwiftUI\/documentation\/OpenSwiftUI\/Image","isActive":true,"type":"reference"},{"type":"text","text":" or "},{"identifier":"doc:\/\/OpenSwiftUI\/documentation\/OpenSwiftUI\/Button","isActive":true,"type":"reference"},{"type":"text","text":" rather"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"than container views such as "},{"identifier":"doc:\/\/OpenSwiftUI\/documentation\/OpenSwiftUI\/VStack","isActive":true,"type":"reference"},{"type":"text","text":" or "},{"identifier":"doc:\/\/OpenSwiftUI\/documentation\/OpenSwiftUI\/HStack","isActive":true,"type":"reference"},{"type":"text","text":". The"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"transformation applies to all child views within this view; calling"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"transaction(_:)"},{"type":"text","text":" on a container view can lead to unbounded scope of"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"execution depending on the depth of the view hierarchy."}]}]}],"metadata":{"modules":[{"relatedModules":["OpenSwiftUICore"],"name":"OpenSwiftUI"}],"role":"symbol","extendedModule":"OpenSwiftUICore","platforms":[{"deprecated":false,"unavailable":false,"beta":false,"introducedAt":"13.0","name":"iOS"},{"deprecated":false,"unavailable":false,"beta":false,"introducedAt":"10.15","name":"macOS"},{"deprecated":false,"unavailable":false,"beta":false,"introducedAt":"13.0","name":"tvOS"},{"deprecated":false,"unavailable":false,"beta":false,"introducedAt":"1.0","name":"visionOS"},{"deprecated":false,"unavailable":false,"beta":false,"introducedAt":"6.0","name":"watchOS"}],"externalID":"s:15OpenSwiftUICore4ViewPAAE11transactionyQryAA11TransactionVzcF::SYNTHESIZED::s:15OpenSwiftUICore4PathV","remoteSource":{"fileName":"TransactionModifier.swift","url":"https:\/\/github.com\/OpenSwiftUIProject\/OpenSwiftUI\/blob\/main\/Sources\/OpenSwiftUICore\/Animation\/Transaction\/TransactionModifier.swift#L84"},"roleHeading":"Instance Method","symbolKind":"method","fragments":[{"text":"func","kind":"keyword"},{"text":" ","kind":